# CACF Compliance Checklist (Operational Template)

## Purpose
This checklist operationalizes the **Constitutional AI Compliance Framework (CACF)** for use by ministries, agencies, and vendors. It provides a **step-by-step validation tool** before procurement, deployment, or scaling of AI systems.

---

## Section 1 – Constitutional Anchors

| Parameter            | Validation Question                                                   | Status (✔/✘) | Notes |
|----------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------|-------|
| **Equality**         | Does the system demonstrate demographic parity (≤5% variance)?        |              |       |
| **Non-Discrimination** | Have automated bias tests been conducted across all protected groups? |              |       |
| **Life & Dignity**   | Has a dignity impact assessment been completed?                       |              |       |
| **Linguistic Justice** | Is the system available in all 22 scheduled languages?               |              |       |
| **Transparency**     | Is the explainability index ≥80% for critical outputs?                |              |       |
| **Privacy**          | Does the system comply with data retention and privacy laws?          |              |       |

---

## Section 2 – IndiaAI Competency Alignment

| Competency Type  | Checklist Item                                                | Status (✔/✘) | Notes |
|------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|--------------|-------|
| **Behavioral**   | Have developers/operators been trained in ethics & curiosity? |              |       |
| **Functional**   | Is procurement tied to CACF audit certification?              |              |       |
| **Domain-Specific** | Has the system passed sectoral tests (health, agri, banking)? |              |       |

---

## Section 3 – Research Protocols

| Protocol                  | Checklist Item                                                            | Status (✔/✘) | Notes |
|---------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------|-------|
| **Federated Learning**    | Is federated training implemented for sensitive datasets?                  |              |       |
| **Bias Mitigation**       | Are ongoing fairness audits scheduled (≤5% demographic variance)?          |              |       |
| **Emergency Override**    | Is a kill-switch protocol in place for critical infrastructure AI?         |              |       |
| **Blockchain Verification** | Are immutable logs and verifiable credentials implemented?                |              |       |

---

## Section 4 – Governance & Accountability

| Governance Item           | Checklist Item                                               | Status (✔/✘) | Notes |
|---------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|--------------|-------|
| **Oversight Body**        | Has the system been registered with NITI Aayog/CACF board?   |              |       |
| **Audit Schedule**        | Has a quarterly audit plan been created?                     |              |       |
| **Escalation Protocol**   | Are violations reportable to a parliamentary or state body?  |              |       |
| **Citizen Grievance**     | Is there an RTI-based appeal mechanism in place?             |              |       |

---

